Class Results

  • java.lang.Object
    • tss.Results

  • public class Results
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for generating the reports of the results for Individuals, Teams and Married Couples. Uses the JasperReports library.
    Author:
    Alex Cordaro

        tournamentID - the id of the tournament
        round - the round to use for the teams

        mixedGender - whether the results will use mixed genders
